          "Some additional information that would be obtainable from the registration form is not included (e.g. TOEFL subscores or additional schools).\n\nAuthors used conditional means to identify potentially relevant features. \n\nClass imbalance is addressed using Bagging. Authors also use GS to perform hyper-parameter optimization.\n\nCategoricals (e.g. Program are OHE\n",
