    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-807e-9135-c6c345c37447",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use Admission Data to predict success of students attending a MSc in Data Science. The paper includes an interpretation of key predictors and multiple classifiers are compared in the task of predicting very good performance from very bad performance on the MSc. ",
